#: ../../output.md:1
msgid "Output parameters"
msgstr "输出参数"

#: ../../output.md:3
msgid "Output and input/output"
msgstr "输出和输入/输出"

#: ../../output.md:5
msgid ""
"For simplicity, and because Javascript only has value semantics for "
"primitive types, Koffi can marshal out (or in/out) multiple types of "
"parameters:"
msgstr ""
"出于简便, 以及由于Javascript的原始值只有值语义, Koffi可以以输出(或输入/输出)转换以下类型的参数:"

#: ../../output.md:7
msgid "[Structs](input.md#struct-types) (to/from JS objects)"
msgstr "[结构体](input.md#struct-types)(转换为/自JS对象)"

#: ../../output.md:8
msgid "[Unions](unions.md)"
msgstr "[联合](unions.md)"

#: ../../output.md:9
msgid "[Opaque types](input.md#opaque-types)"
msgstr "[不透明类型](input.md#opaque-types)"

#: ../../output.md:10
msgid "String buffers"
msgstr "字符串缓冲"

#: ../../output.md:12
msgid ""
"In order to change an argument from input-only to output or input/output,"
" use the following functions:"
msgstr ""
"为了将参数从仅输入变为输出或输入/输出, 使用下列函数:"

#: ../../output.md:14
msgid ""
"`koffi.out()` on a pointer, e.g. `koffi.out(koffi.pointer(timeval))` "
"(where timeval is a struct type)"
msgstr ""
"对指针使用`koffi.out()`, 例如`koffi.out(koffi.pointer(timeval))`(timeval是一个结构体类型)"

#: ../../output.md:15
msgid "`koffi.inout()` for dual input/output parameters"
msgstr "使用`koffi.inout()`来构造同时输入/输出的参数"

#: ../../output.md:17
msgid ""
"The same can be done when declaring a function with a C-like prototype "
"string, with the MSDN-like type qualifiers:"
msgstr ""
"以上也可以在以C风格的原型字符串声明函数中使用MSDN风格的类型限定符:"

#: ../../output.md:19
msgid "`_Out_` for output parameters"
msgstr "使用`_Out_`来表示输出参数"

#: ../../output.md:20
msgid "`_Inout_` for dual input/output parameters"
msgstr "使用`_Inout_`来表示同时输入/输出的参数`"

#: ../../output.md:22
msgid "Primitive value"
msgstr "原始值"

#: ../../output.md:24
msgid ""
"This Windows example enumerate all Chrome windows along with their PID "
"and their title. The `GetWindowThreadProcessId()` function illustrates "
"how to get a primitive value from an output argument."
msgstr ""
"这个Windows的例子枚举所有的Chrome窗口并获取它们的PID和标题. 函数`GetWindowThreadProcessId()`展示了如何从输出参数中获取一个原始值."

#: ../../output.md:78
msgid "Struct example"
msgstr "结构体示例"

#: ../../output.md:80
msgid ""
"This example calls the POSIX function `gettimeofday()`, and uses the "
"prototype-like syntax."
msgstr ""
"这个例子调用了POSIX函数`gettimeofday()`, 并且使用了原型风格的语法."

#: ../../output.md:106
msgid "Opaque type example"
msgstr "不透明类型示例"

#: ../../output.md:108
msgid ""
"This example opens an in-memory SQLite database, and uses the node-ffi-"
"style function declaration syntax."
msgstr ""
"这个例子打开了一个内存中SQLite数据库, 并且使用node-ffi风格的函数声明语法."

#: ../../output.md:133
msgid "String buffer example"
msgstr "字符串缓冲示例"

#: ../../output.md:135
msgid "*New in Koffi 2.2*"
msgstr "*Koffi 2.2引入*"

#: ../../output.md:137
msgid ""
"This example calls a C function to concatenate two strings to a pre-"
"allocated string buffer. Since JS strings are immutable, you must pass an"
" array with a single string instead."
msgstr ""
"这个例子调用了一个C函数来拼接两个字符串到一个预分配的字符串缓冲中. 由于JS字符串是不可变的, 你必须传入一个包含一个字符串的数组."
